CustomField.description: This field is optional and can be collected as part of a workflow. It is the interest rate of the deposit account. If an initial rate (for example, a teaser) applies, then this is the rate that is in effect after the expiration of the teaser period.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: The interest rate of the deposit account. If an initial rate (i.e. a teaser) applies this is the rate that is in effect after the expiration of the teaser period.
CustomField.label: Interest Rate
